{"type":null,"faqId":43498,"title":"添加/取消闹钟","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">时钟，选择屏幕上放的“闹钟”页，进入闹钟界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">选择屏幕左下角的 添加闹钟，进入设置闹钟界面，可以进行如下操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">点击时间，设置闹钟铃响的时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">点击重复，选择需要闹钟重复的周期。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">点击铃声，选择闹钟铃声。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">勾选振动，设置手机在闹钟铃响时振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">点击标签，输入闹钟时间名称。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">点击右上角对号，完成闹钟的添加。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">在闹钟界面，可以看到当前所有闹钟的列表，在每条闹钟记录后面有开关按钮，向左滑动，按钮置灰，显示为关闭，就表示取消了这个闹钟。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">长按一条闹钟记录，在弹出的删除列表中，点击对应闹钟项的红色删除图标，完成删除。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8999","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399018000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"闹钟","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}